(1)Neekerbeekers&#39; Bog(11S249)  (Another option is to run Cavern Entrance in this slot)<br />
(2)Chamber of Mazarbul(11S233)<br />
(2)<!--226-->Moria Stairway(11S248)<br />
(2)West Gate of Moria(11S263)<br />
(3) Mount Doom(15R193)<br />
(3)Moria Guardroom(11S247)<br />
<br />
Fellowship (36)<br />
1x *Ring of Accretion(9R6)<br />
2x *Ring of Fury(9R+7)<br />
2x *Ring of Guile(9R8)<br />
